OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782674291
OL,3,CBad Bunny becomes first artist from
OL,4,CLatin America to headline a UK stadium
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FBad Bunny put on a history-making show
OL,8,Fat Tottenham Hotspur Stadium on
OL,9,FSaturday night, becoming the first
OL,10,FLatin American artist to headline a UK
OL,11,Fstadium show.
OL,13,FThe Puerto Rican rapper preformed to a
OL,14,Fcrowd of 50 thousand people during the
OL,15,Ffirst of two sold-out shows in London,
OL,16,Fcelebrating Central and South American
OL,17,Fculture throughout his set.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
