SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782674291
OL,3,CBad Bunny becomes first artist from
OL,4,CLatin America to headline a UK stadium
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FBad Bunny also paid tribute to those
OL,8,Fwho lost loved ones in the devastating
OL,9,FVenezuelan earthquakes that hit the
OL,10,Fcountry on Wednesday.
OL,12,F"All Latinos around the world stand in
OL,13,Fsolidarity with you," he said.
OL,15,FBenito Antonio Martinez Ocasio, who
OL,16,Fgoes by the stage name Bad Bunny, is
OL,17,Fon the final leg of his Debi Tirar Mas
OL,18,FFotos world tour, playing cities
OL,19,Facross Europe.
