OL,3,CBad Bunny becomes first artist from
OL,4,CLatin America to headline a UK stadium
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FThe album, by the same name, won album
OL,8,Fof the year at the Grammys, becoming
OL,9,Fthe first album sung completely in
OL,10,FSpanish to do so.
OL,12,FBad Bunny has skyrocketed in
OL,13,Fpopularity since the late 2010s has
OL,14,Fnow hit the mainstream as one of the
OL,15,Fmost-streamed artists in the world.
