OL,3,CBad Bunny becomes first artist from
OL,4,CLatin America to headline a UK stadium
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FThe 32-year-old performed at the
OL,8,FSuperbowl earlier this year, bringing
OL,9,FLady Gaga on stage during the halftime
OL,10,Fshow at Super Bowl LX between the
OL,11,FSeattle Seahawks and New England
OL,12,FPatriots.
